nooru janmaku ( kannada : ನೂರು ಜನ ಮಕು ) is a 2010 indian kannada language romantic drama film written and directed by nagathihalli chandrashekar and produced by vinay lad . nagathihalli 's usual associate mano murthy is the music composer for the film . the film stars newcomer santhosh along with aindrita ray and adarsh balakrishna of iqbal fame . the film deals with the recession as the backdrop . santosh rai pathaje is the cinematographer for the film . the film released on 21 may 2010 across karnataka and set high expectations for its storyline and some controversies . however upon release , the film generally met with negative reviews from the critics and audience .